Enum Class ModernDigitalEra

net.xmercerweiss.mdc.ModernDigitalEra
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ModernDigitalEra>, Constable, Era, TemporalAccessor, TemporalAdjuster
public enum ModernDigitalEra extends Enum<ModernDigitalEra> implements Era, Serializable
The eras of the Modern Digital Calendar system as enumerated constants

The Modern Digital Calendar only has 2 era, Before Epoch and Since Epoch, with the epoch being 1970 ISO. The epoch is year 0, and is always considered Since Epoch for simplicity. The year 2000 ISO is 30 SE, and 1900 ISO is 70 BE.
